Technical Information
---------------------

Hardware:
  - Sun Sparc or HP 700 architecture. 
  - Min 8 Mb memory
  - 10 Mb free disk space

Software:
  - SunOS 4.1.x, SunOS 5.3 or greater, HPUX 9.0x. 
  - GNU Emacs 

Content of delivery:
  - Syntax checker
  - Static semantics analyzer
  - Latex generator
  - Interpreter
  - Debugger
  - Test coverage tool
  - Emacs-based development environment

Documentation includes:
  - Language reference manual
  - Quick reference card
  - Users manual for the VDM-SL Toolbox
  - User manual for the DMtoC++ Code Generator
  - The VDM C++ Library 
  - Examples

Optional add-on feature:
  - VDM-SL to C++ code generation including C++ libraries


Til FME:

 * Sun Sparc running SunOS 4.1.x or SunOS 5.3
 * A colour screen
 * Min. 150 Mb free disk space (initial guess)
 * Min.  16 Mb memory
